This paper is primarily focused on computer vision (CV) and machine learning (LG) techniques for high resolution face completion. The paper also discusses the use of loss functions and network architectures, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (AI) research. Additionally, the paper mentions a pilot human study, which suggests a potential connection to multimedia (MM) and graphics (GR) research. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, and cs.GR.
